  if (e.viewTransition) {
    // Dynamically set view-transition-names based on navigation
    // e.viewTransition.ready.then(() => { ... });
  }
});
```

## Browser Support

Cross-document view transitions are supported in **Chrome 126+** and **Edge 126+** (Chromium-based browsers). As of mid-2024, Firefox and Safari do not yet support the `@view-transition` at-rule for cross-document transitions.
