### CSS
```css
/* 1. Define the anchor element */
.anchor-button {
  /* Establish a unique anchor name using a dashed-ident */
  anchor-name: --my-button-anchor;

  /* Standard styling */
  padding: 10px 20px;
  font-size: 16px;
  margin: 100px auto;
  display: block;
}

